imdb.plot outline: The Hulfish Project is an authentic documentary style series about renowned artist Jason Hulfish and his one-of-a-kind creations. This video series documents Hulfish-professionally, yet humorously-on his adventures designing innovative masterpieces and traveling the globe to install them. We hope you'll come with us as we follow Hulfish on this worldwide journey.
